<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #2d3748; background-color: #f7fafc; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .wrapper { padding: 40px 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
        .header { padding: 30px; border-bottom: 2px solid #edf2f7; text-align: left; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 20px; color: #1a202c; letter-spacing: -0.025em; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .footer { padding: 20px 30px; background: #f8fafc; border-top: 1px solid #edf2f7; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; color: #718096; }
        .amount-box { margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #4a5568; }
        .amount-label { font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: #718096; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .amount-value { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a202c; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #2d3748; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; transition: background-color 0.2s; }
        .details-grid { margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #edf2f7; padding-top: 20px; }
        .details-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; }
        .details-label { width: 120px; color: #718096; }
        .details-value { font-weight: 600; color: #2d3748; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>BM Manager</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2 style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 20px; color: #1a202c;">Nouvelle déclaration d'avance</h2>
                <p>Bonjour {{ ownerName }},</p>
                <p>Le locataire <strong>{{ locataire.nomComplet }}</strong> a soumis une nouvelle déclaration d'avance sur loyer pour votre approbation.</p>
                
                <div class="amount-box">
                    <div class="amount-label">Montant déclaré</div>
                    <div class="amount-value">{{ avance.montantTotal|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }} Ar</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="details-grid">
                    <div class="details-row">
                        <span class="details-label">Date :</span>
                        <span class="details-value">{{ avance.dateAccord|date('d/m/Y') }}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="details-row">
                        <span class="details-label">Motif :</span>
                        <span class="details-value">{{ avance.motif|default('Aucune observation') }}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Veuillez vous connecter à votre espace pour valider cette transaction.</p>
                
                <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
                    <a href="{{ url('app_avance_index') }}" class="button">Consulter et Valider</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} BM Manager | Système de gestion immobilière</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
